						<div class="postbody">That's a really impressive mockup!<br /><br />The &quot;bright&quot; side is that the PAL chroma merging won't have much of an effect on your mockups, because there's little hue change from scanline to scanline. A little bit of color bleeds into the grey highlights.<br /><br />The down side is that we haven't codified exactly what's going on with the 2C07's weird chroma shift on alternating scanlines, so it's not clear exactly what color the regions of alternating scanlines would look like.</div>

